PBOOKS OPEN SOURCE ACCOUNTING SOFTWARE
======================================

Summary
-------

Pbooks is an open-source, php-based accounting and bookkeeping system. It is
designed for use by small business, and uses the double-entry accounting model.
Licensed under the Affero GPL v3, beta versions are available for download
today, or you can view a public demo accessible from our website.

Requirements
------------

* PHP
* MySQL
* XSLT PHP Extension
* Apache or similar

Support
-------
[PBooks Website](http://www.pbooks.org/)
